[package]
name = "cairo-rs"
license = "MIT"
homepage = "https://gtk-rs.org/"
authors = [ "The gtk-rs Project Developers",]
keywords = [ "cairo", "gtk-rs", "gnome", "GUI",]
readme = "README.md"
documentation = "https://gtk-rs.org/gtk-rs-core/stable/latest/docs/cairo/"
version = "0.17.7"
description = "Rust bindings for the Cairo library"
repository = "https://github.com/gtk-rs/gtk-rs-core"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.64"

[lib]
name = "cairo"

[features]
png = [ "ffi/png",]
pdf = [ "ffi/pdf",]
svg = [ "ffi/svg",]
ps = [ "ffi/ps",]
use_glib = [ "glib", "ffi/use_glib",]
v1_16 = [ "ffi/v1_16",]
v1_18 = [ "v1_16", "ffi/v1_18",]
default = [ "use_glib",]
freetype = [ "ffi/freetype", "freetype-rs",]
script = [ "ffi/script",]
xcb = [ "ffi/xcb",]
xlib = [ "ffi/xlib",]
dox = [ "ffi/dox", "glib/dox", "freetype",]
win32-surface = [ "ffi/win32-surface",]

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2"
bitflags = "1.0"
thiserror = "1.0.10"
once_cell = "1"

[dev-dependencies]
tempfile = "3.0"
float_eq = "1"

[dependencies.glib]
optional = true
path = "../glib"
version = "0.17"

[dependencies.ffi]
package = "cairo-sys-rs"
path = "sys"
version = "0.17"

[dependencies.freetype-rs]
version = "0.32"
optional = true

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "dox",]

[package]
name = "cairo-sys-rs"
license = "MIT"
authors = [ "The gtk-rs Project Developers",]
homepage = "https://gtk-rs.org/"
description = "FFI bindings to libcairo"
version = "0.17.7"
keywords = [ "cairo", "ffi", "gtk-rs", "gnome",]
repository = "https://github.com/gtk-rs/gtk-rs-core"
build = "build.rs"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.64"

[lib]
name = "cairo_sys"

[features]
dox = [ "x11/dox", "glib/dox",]
v1_16 = []
v1_18 = [ "v1_16",]
xlib = [ "x11",]
png = []
pdf = []
svg = []
ps = []
freetype = []
script = []
xcb = []
use_glib = [ "glib",]
win32-surface = [ "winapi",]

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2"

[build-dependencies]
system-deps = "6"

[dependencies.glib]
package = "glib-sys"
optional = true
path = "../../glib/sys"
version = "0.17"

[dependencies.x11]
optional = true
version = "2.16"
features = [ "xlib",]

[package.metadata.system-deps.cairo]
name = "cairo"
version = "1.14"

[package.metadata.system-deps.cairo-gobject]
name = "cairo-gobject"
version = "1.14"
feature = "use_glib"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.winapi]
version = "0.3.2"
features = [ "windef",]

[dev-dependencies.matroska]
